column3: Thanks for fixing those, but I'd prefer if we had a single pull request for those and not separate for each typo (c.f. #13052 from two days ago)

@MarcoFalke I submit typos as I find them (otherwise I would forget them!). If I have an already existing open typo PR then I add the newly found typo to that one. Is that not the recommended procedure? :-)
Fine, I will leave this one open until next month.
> Fine, I will leave this one open until next month.\n\nAgree.
